      "content": "Oh, my bad, I thought you had the document uploaded in our shared workspace. Let me copy-paste the text of Section 4.2 here so you can look at it:\n\n\"4.2 Price Adjustments: SwiftRoute agrees to the base rates established in Appendix A. However, during peak demand months (November through February), the Supplier reserves the right to implement a price adjustment of up to 5% at their sole discretion, without prior written notice to SwiftRoute, to account for market volatility.\"\n\nCan you confirm if that allows them to hike prices unexpectedly? I really need a definitive yes or no so I can report back to my boss that our costs are locked in.",
